# Authors

This file is the authoritative record of authorship for the Nimbus-C2
project. Contributors who have accepted the `CONTRIBUTING.md`
process and had code merged are listed here in order of first merged
contribution.

## Original author and project lead

Maria Westrin — Stockholm, SE
   Original concept, architecture, scoring formulation, assurance model,
   MILP weapon-target-assignment formulation, conformal-prediction
   gating layer, safety-shield specification, repository and
   release management.

## Contributors

None yet. Contributions welcome — see `CONTRIBUTING.md`.

## Citation

When citing this work, cite the repository as a whole (see `CITATION.cff`
for the canonical form). Individual authorship of specific modules is
recorded per-file via SPDX headers and in the git history; `git blame`
and `git log --follow <file>` give the fine-grained record.

## Contact

Security issues: see `SECURITY.md`.
General questions and contributions: GitHub issues and pull requests on
the canonical repository.
